text: Less than a minute into the trailer and they've already got a massive fact cock-up with the nuclear plant.  In reality nuclear power plant control systems are not networked, they're intentionally built to be completely isolated from any outside networks so sabotaging them requires direct access to the facilities they're housed in. So tampering with them is hardly hacker stuff, it's just regular hollywood style terrorism when you need to physically hijack the whole facility first.
